Tanzanian singer Zuchu says that Diamond Platnumz knows who she is dating. In Valentine's event, "Mahaba Ndi Ndi Ndi' the 'Sukari' hitmaker said." "Diamond knows my boyfriend." Asked why he decided to walk the red carpet with her, Diamond said, "Mtoto kwa baba hakui," she said. "Zuchu is my artiste, it is not the first time I'm attending a red carpet with her. "The first time was when I was launching her. When I first brought her here, she was a child, right now she is big." Diamond was then asked whether he knew the boyfriend was going to propose to Zuchu. "People who are in love can do many things, as a leader is just to agree with what happens. As long as my artiste is happy, I am happy."